James Roaf
 International Monetary Fund(I.M.F)
 Senior Regional Resident Representative
 37C Zielna, 00-108
 Warszawa, Poland
www.imf.org
  Attention:- THE IMMEDIATE FAMILY MEMBERS OF THE BENEFICIARY

Respected People .

  We got information on the death of the beneficiary . Our sincere
condolences to You, the wife ,children and immediate family
members. May God repay your loss Amen. However, we are very surprised
that the beneficiary changed his next of kin and inheritor as MRS.
Victoria Kujiper from Holland. We hope the family knows about this. We
shall instruct the new Head auditor of the World bank to commence the
process of transferring the inheritance to MRS. Victoria Kujiper  by
next month if there is no challenge from your family. The new WORLD BANK
AUDITORS  are now in-charge of all payments.You can contact the Head
auditor of the world bank directly on his email address  -
moncabrown444@gmail.com. Her name is MS. Monica Brown  if you have issues
with that. Once again accept our sincere condolence. May the soul of the
beneficiary rest in peace Amen.

Thank you

Regards
 .
 james Roaf
 International Monetary Fund(I.M.F)
 Senior Regional Resident Representative
 37C Zielna, 00-108
 Warszawa, Poland
